05:32.249 --> 05:33.534
[WIND HOWLS]

05:33.709 --> 05:35.245
[THUD]

05:36.086 --> 05:37.417
[MAN GROANING]

05:41.883 --> 05:45.626
WOMAN [OVER RADIO]: All cars
