MAN:
Are you all right?

06:11.163 --> 06:12.494
WOMAN:
Okay.

06:14.916 --> 06:16.907
WOMAN: Somebody help.
MAN: Okay.

06:25.677 --> 06:29.636
WOMAN:
Please help me. He's not breathing.

06:31.808 --> 06:33.469
Davis?

06:33.643 --> 06:35.508
[PEOPLE SPEAKING |ND|ST|NCTLY]

