or any kind of explosion.

07:05.884 --> 07:09.797
-Did something attack these people?
-I don't know. I, uh....

07:10.222 --> 07:13.635
-l was walking with take out.
-You don't remember coming in here?

07:13.809 --> 07:14.844
The screams?

07:16.686 --> 07:17.971
No.

07:19.189 --> 07:20.850
